<tal:block tal:define="dummy python:request.set('span_class', 'col-md-9');
"><html
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      lang="en"
      metal:use-macro="context/main_template/macros/master"
      i18n:domain="plone">

    <metal:no-ads fill-slot="column_two_slot"/>
    <metal:no-ads fill-slot="ad-block-above-content"/>

    <metal:block fill-slot="top_slot"
                 tal:define="dummy python:request.set('disable_border', 1)" />

    <metal:block fill-slot="head_slot">
        <script type="text/javascript"
                tal:condition="python:0"
                src="/++resource++unitracccourse/course_view.js"></script>
    </metal:block>

<body>
    <!-- Fülle Breadcrumbs -->
    <metal:block fill-slot="breadcrumb">
        <metal:block metal:use-macro="context/crumbs/macros/main"/>
    </metal:block>

    <!-- Fülle Navigation -->
    <metal:block metal:fill-slot="column_one_slot"/>

    <!-- Fülle Inhalt -->
<tal:comment replace="nothing"><!--

Bei fehlerhaften Werten für die UID (hier leider: cuid) kann ggf. unitracccourse.get_uid
bzw. (wegen des abweichenden Namens) eine davon abgeleitete Methode verwendet werden.
Frage: ergibt der Rückfallwert "| nothing" hier einen Sinn?!

--></tal:comment>
    <metal:main fill-slot="main">
        <div class="area-content"
         tal:define="
uid            request/form/cuid | nothing;
unitracccourse nocall:here/@@unitracccourse;
brain          python:unitracccourse.get_brain_by_uid(uid);
here           python:unitracccourse.get_current(uid);
title          brain/Title;
text           brain/getCourse_documents_text;
">
            <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <h1 tal:content="structure title">
                    Kurstitel
                </h1>
                <tal:if-has-text condition="text">
                <div tal:define="transform nocall:here/@@transform"
                     tal:content="structure python:transform.get(text)">
                Hier der Hinweistext für die Kursdokumente
                </div>
                </tal:if-has-text>
                <div tal:condition="not:text"
                     i18n:translate="">
                Sorry, no course documents available yet.
                </div>
            </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </metal:main>

</body>
</html>
</tal:block>
